    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents a base decorator for defence items, allowing additional behavior to be layered on top of an existing <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1defence_1_1_defence_item" kindref="compound">DefenceItem</ref> instance. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class implements the Decorator Design Pattern. It wraps another <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1defence_1_1_defence_item" kindref="compound">DefenceItem</ref> and forwards all property calls to the wrapped item unless overridden by subclasses. Concrete decorators can modify <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1defence_1_1_defence_decorator_1a917713af7125e4c222a7a943af0cd9cc" kindref="member">Weight</ref>, <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1defence_1_1_defence_decorator_1a7b9186d2e96f90e1f38021b06e4866e3" kindref="member">ReduceDamage</ref>,or other behavior without changing the underlying item. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
